headline: United Airlines flight evacuated after engine sparks fire on wing during takeoff at Houston airport
summary: HOUSTON — Passengers were evacuated via slides and stairs from a jetliner at Houston's main airport on Sunday after an engine problem during takeoff caused smoke and fire on the right wing. ...
